          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='1' fontname='Tableau Medium'>Priority Tier Distribution</run>
            <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#666666' fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='11'>The most common outreach angle is logistics but priority 1 need logistics + communication support</run>
