    <dashboard enable-sort-zone-taborder='true' name='Home'>
      <layout-options>
        <title>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='1' fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='24'>Olist Seller Risk Monitor</run>
            <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#666666' fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='15'>Seller Success Team · Olist Operations</run>
            <run fontalignment='1' fontsize='9'>Æ </run>
            <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#666666' fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='11'>Data period: September 2016 – October 2018</run>
            <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#666666' fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='11'>Scored population: 1,238 sellers · At Risk: 186 sellers (15.0%)</run>
            <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='1' fontsize='9'>Æ </run>
            <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='15'>How To Use This Workbook</run>
            <run fontalignment='1' fontsize='12'>Æ </run>
            <run fontalignment='1' fontsize='9'>Æ  </run>
            <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='11'>Platform Health Overview:</run>
            <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='1' fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='11'>Executive summary of the At Risk seller population for the Head of Operations. Shows intervention priority breakdown, dominant failure modes, and geographic distribution of At Risk sellers.</run>
            <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='11'>At Risk Seller Explorer:</run>
            <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='1' fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='11'>Filter and identify at risk sellers for outreach. Sort by intervention priority and health score. </run>
            <run fontalignment='1' fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='11' underline='true'>Click any row to open the full seller profile</run>
            <run fontalignment='1' fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='11'>.</run>
            <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='11'>Seller Profile:</run>
            <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='1' fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='11'>Full profile for outreach preparation. Accessed by clicking a seller row in the Explorer. Shows performance metrics, complaint profile, flags, and recommended intervention.</run>
            <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='1' fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='11'>Æ </run>
          </formatted-text>
        </title>
      </layout-options>
      <style />
      <size maxheight='1160' maxwidth='1420' minheight='1160' minwidth='1420' sizing-mode='range' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='100000' id='4' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
          <zone h='98620' id='7' param='vert' type-v2='layout-flow' w='98874' x='563' y='690'>
            <zone h='44138' id='8' type-v2='title' w='98874' x='563' y='690'>
              <zone-style>
                <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                <format attr='margin' value='4' />
              </zone-style>
            </zone>
            <zone fixed-size='617' forceUpdate='true' h='53880' id='21' is-fixed='true' type-v2='text' w='98874' x='563' y='44828'>
              <formatted-text>
                <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='15'>Key Concepts</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='11'>Health Score: </run>
                <run fontcolor='#333333' fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='11'>Each seller is assigned a Health Score — a composite 0 to 100 measure of seller performance calculated from four dimensions: average review score (every order has a 1-5 star score) (40%), late order rate (28%), 1-star review rate (22%), and average delivery days (10%). Each dimension is percentile-ranked within the scoreable population so that scores reflect relative performance rather than absolute values. Higher scores indicate healthier sellers.</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#333333' fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='11'>Only sellers with 10 or more delivered orders are included in scoring.</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#14181f' fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='11'>At Risk Sellers: </run>
                <run fontcolor='#14181f' fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='11'>Æ </run>
                <run fontcolor='#333333' fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='11'>Sellers with a Health score in the bottom 15%  (186 sellers) </run>
                <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='11'>Complaint Categories:</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='11'>Æ </run>
                <run fontcolor='#333333' fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='11'>Negative reviews (1–2 star) with written comments from At Risk sellers were analysed using keyword-based complaint categorisation across six failure types: Non-Delivery, Delivery Delay, Wrong Product, Product Quality, Poor Communication, and Poor Packaging. </run>
                <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='11'>Intervention Priority and Dominant Complaint Category: </run>
                <run fontcolor='#333333' fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='11'>Each seller&apos;s distribution of complaint types across their negative reviews was used to identify their dominant complaint category (Their most common complaint category) and assign an intervention priority tier:</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#333333' fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='11'>Priority 1 — Immediate (Delivery + communication) is assigned if the seller received delivery AND communication complaints. </run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#333333' fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='11'>Priority 2 — Logistics and 3 — Product are assigned depending on if the sellers dominant category was delivery or product related. </run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#333333' fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='11'>Priority 4 — Review is assigned if customer feedback was insufficient, these sellers should be evaluated individually. </run>
                <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#333333' fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='11' italic='true'>Complaint categorisation was conducted in Portuguese using prefix stemming and keyword matching. Category precision was validated through manual review of translated samples (minimum 70% precision threshold). 40% of negative reviews with comments were not categorised — predominantly short emotional expressions and idiomatic language.</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontalignment='1' fontname='Tableau Medium'>Analysis conducted by Samuel Walker · Olist Brazilian E-Commerce Dataset (Kaggle) · Built in Tableau Public</run>
              </formatted-text>
              <zone-style>
                <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                <format attr='margin' value='4' />
              </zone-style>
            </zone>
          </zone>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <format attr='margin' value='8' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
      </zones>
      <devicelayouts>
